"title": "8608: prayer, and worship",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8608: prayer, and worship",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Worship is turning to God in awe, praise and joy, as his people realise how wonderful he is. Prayer is a natural part of worship: to know God is to want to worship him and pray to him.</p>\n<h2>Worship is a fundamental requirement of life</h2>\n<h3>All nations are exhorted to worship God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:28-1Chr16:29\">1CH 16:28–16:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:1-Ps29:2\">PSA 29:1–29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:9\">PSA 96:9</a></p>\n<h3>Israel is commanded to worship God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:36\">2KI 17:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:6-Ps95:7\">PSA 95:6–95:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:4-Ps99:5\">PSA 99:4–99:5</a></p>\n<h2>Right attitudes in worship are imperative</h2>\n<h3>Reverence and humility characterise acceptable worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28-Heb12:29\">HEB 12:28–12:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:7\">PSA 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:6\">PSA 95:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:2\">PSA 138:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:1\">ECC 5:1</a></p>\n<h3>Honesty, without hypocrisy, characterises acceptable worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21-Amos5:24\">AMO 5:21–5:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:7-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:7–15:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6-Mark7:7\">MRK 7:6–7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:24\">JHN 4:24</a></p>\n<h2>Prayer can focus on different aspects of God's character</h2>\n<h3>Prayer can focus on God's holiness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:11\">EXO 15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:13\">PSA 77:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:9\">PSA 96:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:5\">PSA 99:5</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer can focus on God's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:6\">PSA 19:1–19:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:1-Ps29:2\">PSA 29:1–29:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:5\">PSA 138:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:27\">ROM 16:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:20\">PHP 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:25\">JUD 1:25</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer can focus on God's majesty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:1-Ps104:4\">PSA 104:1–104:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:1\">PSA 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:4\">PSA 76:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:4-Ps96:6\">PSA 96:4–96:6</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer can focus on God's kingship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:1\">PSA 97:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:7\">PSA 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:3\">PSA 22:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:1\">PSA 93:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:3\">PSA 95:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:12\">PSA 102:12</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer can focus on God's love and compassion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:1-Ps103:18\">PSA 103:1–103:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:4\">PSA 111:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:1-Ps118:4\">PSA 118:1–118:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:17-Ps145:20\">PSA 145:17–145:20</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer can focus on God's justice and righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:2\">PSA 97:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:17\">PSA 7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:8\">PSA 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:6\">PSA 97:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:3\">PSA 111:3</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer can focus on God's creative activity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:6\">NEH 9:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:2\">PSA 90:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:3-Ps95:7\">PSA 95:3–95:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:25-Ps102:27\">PSA 102:25–102:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:5-Ps104:9\">PSA 104:5–104:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:24-Ps104:26\">PSA 104:24–104:26</a></p>",
